ex:utteranceText_dd_0_0 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Say , Jim , how about going for a few beers after dinner ?"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceText_dd_0_1 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "You know that is tempting but is really not good for our fitness ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceText_dd_0_2 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "What do you mean ? It will help us to relax ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceText_dd_0_3 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Do you really think so ? I don't . It will just make us fat and act silly . Remember last time ?"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceText_dd_0_4 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "I guess you are right.But what shall we do ? I don't feel like sitting at home ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceText_dd_0_5 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "I suggest a walk over to the gym where we can play singsong and meet some of our friends ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceText_dd_0_6 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "That's a good idea . I hear Mary and Sally often go there to play pingpong.Perhaps we can make a foursome with them ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceText_dd_0_7 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Sounds great to me ! If they are willing , we could ask them to go dancing with us.That is excellent exercise and fun , too ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceText_dd_0_8 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Good.Let ' s go now ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceText_dd_0_9 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "All right ."^^xsd:string .

